   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1664_dai_lns235ms_d1_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                     <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازش خان</persName>
                     <unclear>اخلاص</unclear>
                     <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">اورنگزیب</persName>
                      بادشاه غازی</mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبدۃ الاقران چودری
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
                بعنایت و مھربانی امیدوار بودہ بداند عرضہ داشتی
               <lb/>کہ درین ولا ارسال داشتہ بود بنظر در آمد باید کہ پسر خود را بتحصیل مقید و سرگرم
               ساختہ
               <lb/>با جمعیت سوار و پیادہ بحضور بیاید اگر در تحصیل سستی بوقوع خواھد آمد
               <lb/>نتیجہ نیک نخواھد یافت و عذر او مسموع نگشتہ وجہ بقایا
               <choice>
                  <expan>از او</expan>
                  <abbr>ازو</abbr>
               </choice>
                باز یافت
               <lb/>خواھد گردید درین باب تاکید دانستہ در آمدن خود اھمل
               <lb/>ننماید تحریرا في التاریخ دوازدہ و یکم
               <lb/>شھر شوال سنہ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>۱۰٧۴</num></date>
               ھجری مطابق
               سنہ
               <date calendar="#julus"><num>۷</num></date>
               حکومت والا
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="bottom right margin">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>حسب المسطور مقرر دانستہ
               <lb/>بموجب فرمودہ عمل نماید بزودی زود
               <lb/> خود را بحضور رساند مجری خود داند
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1664_dai_lns235ms_d1_v.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right">
            <p>
               <lb/>پروانہ بندگان نواب مستطاب
               <lb/>کہ بھمل پسر خود را برای
               <lb/>تاکید تحصیل پرگنہ
               <lb/>گزاشتہ خود بمھم حسب
               <app>
                  <rdg cert="low">پوری</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="medium">لوای</rdg>
               </app>
               <lb/>با جماعه خود بیاید </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div7" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top centre">
            <p>
               <foreign>نمبر</foreign>
               <num>۵٨</num>
            </p>
         </div>


         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>
               <unclear>sincere disciple</unclear>
                of
               <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Aurangzeb</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_badshah">Badshah</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_ghazi">Ghazi</ref>
            </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref>
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam [Das]</persName>, having hoped for kindness and grace, know that the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">ʿarz-dasht</ref>
               <lb/>that recently had been sent has come to [our] attention. It is necessary that having
               appointed and engaged [your] own son in the collection of revenues
               <lb/>he [i.e. <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>] comes to the Lord with [his] company of horsemen and foot soldiers. If there occurs
               any laziness in the collection [of revenues],
               <lb/>the results will not be good. His excuses will not be heard, and deductions for the arrears will be taken from him.
               <lb/>Knowing this  matter to be confirmed, do not neglect to come. 
               <lb/>Written on the <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">12 and 1st
               [i.e. the 13th]
               <lb/>of the month of Shawwal of the year 1074 Hijri</date> corresponding to <date calendar="#julus">year 7 of the
               exalted reign</date>.<note>13 Shawwal 1074 occurred in the last month of Regnal Year 6, not Regnal Year 7 as written in the document. The date has been
                  converted to Gregorian using the Hijri year given in the document.</note>
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p><lb/>Knowing it to be confirmed as written, 
               <lb/>he should do as ordered. As soon as possible,
               <lb/>he should deliver himself to the Lord. He himself knows what is to be done.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div6" xml:id="trans_div6">
            <p><lb/>The <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">parvana</ref> of the servants of the Eminent <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nawab">Nawab</ref>: 
               <lb/>that having burdened his own son with<note>In other words, having made his son responsible for the tax collection.</note>
               <lb/>the collection of taxes of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref><note>The pargana in question is likely <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName> although it is unnamed in the document.</note>
               <lb/>with importance <unclear>according to the banner</unclear>,
               <lb/>he should come with his company [of soldiers].</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div7" xml:id="trans_div7">
            <p>Number 57</p>
         </div>
      </body>
